data.description: Stunning 2020-built home in the beautiful Driftwood Ranch Subdivision! This immaculate 3-bed, 2-bath gem boasts a spacious open floor plan with upgraded tile throughout (except bedrooms), creating a sleek and modern feel. The extra-large den is perfect for a home office or entertainment space. Enjoy a beautifully landscaped front and backyard, a haven for outdoor enthusiasts. The 3-car garage provides ample storage. Don't miss the chance to make this contemporary oasis yours!
